[SN]TITLE[SN]
Plans for Velindre Cancer Centre in Whitchurch, Cardiff

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An outline planning application is due to be submitted for a new cancer centre in Cardiff.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Velindre NHS Trust wants to build a new Velindre Cancer Centre on land north of Whitchurch Hospital playing fields.
It would include a specialist cancer treatment centre, facilities for learning, research and development.
Access is proposed from the Coryton interchange and emergency access via Hollybush Estate.
